#!/usr/bin/env runprompt
---
model: openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2
tools:
  - real_debrid.get_links
  - real_debrid.append_download_link
files:
  - CONVENTIONS.md
---
Fetch the Real-Debrid downloads list using get_links.

{{#if INPUT}}
Only process links that belong to the series: "{{INPUT}}". Skip everything else.
{{else}}
Process all links.
{{/if}}

For each relevant download link, determine the series name and season, then call append_download_link for each one. The tool will handle creating folders and the download.sh file automatically.
